&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Inside Salesperson will work with clients to provide a successful customer experience. The Inside Salesperson will generate sales of all product lines offered.&amp;nbsp;Will work with existing customers and secure prospective new customers and clients by phone, e-mail and direct office appointments providing detailed information on product specifications, services, pricing and delivery and install scheduling.&amp;nbsp;Will focus on designers, remodelers, and select builders as well as retail customers. Will also work showroom hours including Saturdays. A comp day will be provided for Saturday hours.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide an exceptional showroom experience for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct sales presentation of products and services to customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist customers on the showroom floor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in answering phones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist customers over the phone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist customers via email&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend training functions as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and clean specific area of the showroom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect deposits and balances before delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with inventory as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up phone calls to secure orders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in after hour events and sponsorships as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resolve customer issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate and develop new customer business accounts to increase revenue at a profitable level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enter orders into computer system, work with production regarding order, delivery, installation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up to ensure customer satisfaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in collections as necessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competencies/Skills/Abilities&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
